@BASE_URL = http://localhost:3000/api
@API_BASE = https://your-api-gateway-url.amazonaws.com
@X_API_KEY = secret1

### ─── Merchants ───

### Create merchant
POST {{API_BASE}}/core/entity/merchant
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Coffee House",
  "category": "food-beverage",
  "contactEmail": "hello@coffeehouse.com"
}

### Create another merchant
POST {{API_BASE}}/core/entity/merchant
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tech Store",
  "category": "electronics",
  "contactEmail": "support@techstore.com"
}

### ─── Buyers ───

### Create buyer
POST {{API_BASE}}/core/entity/buyer
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com"
}

### ─── Transactions ───

### Create a sale transaction
POST {{API_BASE}}/core/entity/transaction
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "type": "sale",
  "description": "Latte and croissant",
  "transactionDate": "2025-03-15T10:30:00.000Z",
  "status": "completed",
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "buyerId": "{{buyerId}}",
  "merchantIds": ["{{merchantId}}"],
  "buyerIds": ["{{buyerId}}"]
}

### Create a refund transaction
POST {{API_BASE}}/core/entity/transaction
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2000,
  "type": "refund",
  "description": "Wrong order refund",
  "transactionDate": "2025-03-16T14:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "completed",
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "buyerId": "{{buyerId}}",
  "merchantIds": ["{{merchantId}}"],
  "buyerIds": ["{{buyerId}}"]
}

### ─── Tag Queries ───

### All transactions by date range
GET {{API_BASE}}/core/tag/transaction/date?start=2025-03-01&end=2025-03-31
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}

### Transactions by merchant + date range
GET {{API_BASE}}/core/tag/transaction/merchant-date?group={{merchantId}}&start=2025-03-01&end=2025-03-31
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}

### Transactions by buyer + date range
GET {{API_BASE}}/core/tag/transaction/buyer-date?group={{buyerId}}&start=2025-03-01&end=2025-03-31
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}

### Transactions by type
GET {{API_BASE}}/core/tag/transaction/type?group=sale
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}

### ─── Custom Aggregation ───

### Summary for date range
GET {{API_BASE}}/core/app/summary?start=2025-03-01&end=2025-03-31
x-api-key: {{X_API_KEY}}
